formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1) Carpet area provided in certificate is as per date provided by promoter in consultation with project architect.
2) Promoter has availed overdraft facility from Axis Bank Ltd. Said OD used by promoter for both project payment and personal payment as well. It is not practically possible for me to identify, to what extent proportion of interest related to project payment and for personal payment. And hence interest paid on OD was not claimed as expenditure incurred and paid in this certificate and the same ultimately does not result in withdrawal of money from RERA designated account. Details of the same also not provided in lenders column since it's not possible to identify which repayment is related to personal payment and which to project payment.
3) Inadvertently at the time of registration of project, I have provided RERA collection account number as an RERA Bank Account number. Kindly consider, 919020048825017 as RERA Bank Account for the certificate.
4) One AFS is not as per draft provided at the time of registration.
5) Promoter inadvertently failed to deposit Rs. 84,000.00 in her RERA bank account (919020048825017), remaining receipts was deposited in RERA bank account.
6) In case of unsecured loan no formal agreement signed between lender & promoter of project. Details provided is as provided and explained to me by project promoter. Loan details provided on consolidated basis.
